{"id": "1480444697997479977", "channel_id": "1480444697997479977", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "結論 不建議抽\n除非有超高練珊\n\n調查行動-融災禁區·第5波·V級警報——戰鬥回放\n守密人：瑪爾（100018361）\n\n珊、堅韌意志、跨越疼痛、埋骨地絮語\n莫絲、渺遠的伊甸園、記憶螺旋、36室之環\n「24」、畸體回噬、珍饈、四月禮讚\n朵爾、快樂魔法秀、被囚禁的瘋狂、埋骨地絮語\n鼠鼠的智慧\n\n74b06fc5-94d2-3aa0-948a-c600207e98fb#E#a", "timestamp": "2026-03-09T05:58:41.335000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-09T06:17:44.944000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1480444698211385427", "filename": "Screenshot_20260309_130417_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 118997}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480445179818410096", "channel_id": "1480444697997479977", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "我不清楚高練的莫絲能不能力大磚飛 那個還要試\n但至少在莫絲金數不高時\n她最需要的就是撐回合數去成長", "timestamp": "2026-03-09T06:00:36.210000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480446044159475754", "channel_id": "1480444697997479977", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 以下僅是我的體驗分享\n莫絲的傷害是沒有問題的\n暴傷 暴率都有\n但她就很奇妙地 需要一個常駐角去生存跟成長\n所以珊的練度尤為重要", "timestamp": "2026-03-09T06:04:02.285000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480447060330418277", "channel_id": "1480444697997479977", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "那就順便簡單講一下隊伍組成\n珊 莫絲 24 船長\n24:潤滑油\n能生觸手 有易傷虛弱 自充能力還不錯\n船長(可替換):輔助\n易傷虛弱 有盾 不俗的自充能力\n還能洗牌", "timestamp": "2026-03-09T06:08:04.559000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480447536341843979", "channel_id": "1480444697997479977", "type": 0, "author_id": "462595164851011594", "author_name": "elkmilu", "author_bot": false, "content": "跟好夥伴諾締拉有料嗎", "timestamp": "2026-03-09T06:09:58.049000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480447866827837533", "channel_id": "1480444697997479977", "type": 19, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "諾沒有觸傷成長 而且自充能力有點差", "timestamp": "2026-03-09T06:11:16.843000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["462595164851011594"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1480447536341843979", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1480448049913397300", "channel_id": "1480444697997479977", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "我會覺得莫絲表面上沒有綁隊伍\n但實際上就要求隊友都能自己充起來 還要給她提供生存", "timestamp": "2026-03-09T06:12:00.494000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-09T06:12:24.366000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
